name: MYSTICAL PATH
description:
there are many paths to walk, but where to walk if they don't exist? 

maybe it's time for you to make your own way, even if it's bad. 

no need for complicated things, just bring flowers on the trip. 

just look ahead, and keep walking. 

the passage of the past as a form of travel that makes you live, even though sometimes it is terrible. 

love/lose this road.

down the mystical path.
